data.description: This gorgeous tri-level home off is Vista Del Sol and Joe Battle.  with 2 living areas. 2354 sqft of living space. Breakfast and Family room. Bonus room perfect for an office or play area. Kitchen offers tons cabinet space and beautiful granite countertops. Grand primary suite. Double vanities. 2 additional bedrooms with full bath. Fourth bedroom is located downstairs. Seller is willing to sell fully furnished. All offers being considered.
